    "question": "A project manager is working on launching a minimum viable product (MVP) for a new-to-market product. The team has successfully progressed to the third iteration out of a planned total of six. During the upcoming iteration planning meeting, the customer notifies the team that a competitor intends to beat them to market and release a similar product in the next quarter. \nHow should the project manager address this competitive challenge?",
