    "question": "A project manager is handling multiple projects in five different countries and is issued a new directive on workplace attire and office arrangements. This has been met with resistance in three countries, resulting in a series of misunderstandings, resentment, and potential legal issues.\nWhat should the project manager have done to better handle this situation?",
