    "question": "A project manager in the execution phase of a project discovers several stakeholders identified at project initiation are no longer involved. These removed stakeholders are frustrated with unnecessary communication and express concern that the remaining stakeholders may not be receiving all of the information they require.\nWhat should the project manager have done to prevent this situation?",
